WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.740 --> 00:00:05.228
Open up a web browser,
and visit virtualbox.org.

2
00:00:08.167 --> 00:00:09.810
Look for the downloads link.

3
00:00:12.020 --> 00:00:14.970
Now click on the installation file for
your platform.

4
00:00:14.970 --> 00:00:16.970
In this case, we're downloading
the MAC installation file.

5
00:00:20.551 --> 00:00:22.790
Once the download is complete,
open the file.

6
00:00:33.510 --> 00:00:36.580
Now double-click on VirtualBox.pkg.

7
00:00:36.580 --> 00:00:40.720
That will start the installation process.

8
00:00:40.720 --> 00:00:42.400
Click continue.

9
00:00:42.400 --> 00:00:43.530
Click continue again.

10
00:00:44.810 --> 00:00:46.600
You're just going to
accept all the defaults.

11
00:00:46.600 --> 00:00:47.100
Click Install.

12
00:01:00.150 --> 00:01:05.707
At the end of the installation you can
start VirtualBox by opening up the finder,

13
00:01:05.707 --> 00:01:11.280
navigating to the applications folder,
and double-clicking on VirtualBox.

